summary: Startling Luke Skywalker Rumor Will Have You Questioning His Star Wars 9 Return
body:
Startling Luke Skywalker Rumor Will Have You Questioning His Star Wars 9 Return

Ugh, to leak or not to leak.

I don’t want to read leaks, I don’t want anything to be spoiled for me when I watch Episode IX.

But…

It’s like an Itch I have to scratch!

Save me!

title: The New Order
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2OS7jY6

by Bam4Me

Anakin always knew he would be the head of the Sith and Jedi order one day, but the training to take care of so many people is harder than he expected, so, Master Palpatine decides he needs to know what it’s like to take care of one of the most sensitive and small members of the entire order, a little jedi named Obi-Wan.

This is going to be fun.

summary: Star Destroyer models! I’m building my own little fleet. I need to buy and build three or so more of these guys, and then round...
caption: Star Destroyer models! I’m building my own little fleet. I need to buy and build three or so more of these guys, and then round the whole thing out with a Super Star Destroyer. I’m super pleased with the quality of these small guys. I didn’t take any closeups, but the detailing is pretty swell! At six bucks a piece, they’re absolutely a steal. I believe they’re made by Bandai.
